arrangementElements.html:
Westbound motorists travelling on the City West Link will need to merge from right to left instead of left to right, just west of The Crescent intersection. This is a permanent change and came into effect on Tuesday 29 August.


Eastbound motorists approaching Rozelle interchange need to decide 300m sooner which lane to choose, depending on their destination; for Anzac Bridge use the left lane, for Victoria Rd use the right lane.
